!! green dark/light
XTerm*color2: S_green
XTerm*color10: S_base1

!! yellow dark/light
XTerm*color3: S_yellow
XTerm*color11: S_base0

!! blue dark/light
XTerm*color4: S_blue
XTerm*color12: S_base00

!! magenta dark/light
XTerm*color5: S_magenta
XTerm*color13: S_violet

!! cyan dark/light
XTerm*color6: S_cyan
